item.title: Most listened 2019
item.description: I’m always interested in the music that’s the best to come out in any given year, but this often contrasts heavily with my actual listening habits. This is why I look to Last.fm for my top listened to albums of the year. Flume - Hi This Is Flume Flying Lotus - Flamagra Denzel Curry - Zuu Weval - The Weight Vorna - Sateet palata saavat Sensible Soccers - Aurora Behemoth - I Loved You At Your Darkest Borknagar - True North Yagya - Stormur James Blake - Assume Form For reference, my albums of the year 2019.
